Discovered a whole new side of Ibiza from our stay at @7PinesIbiza. From the magic of Es Vedrà & unimaginable sunsets in the west, to the iconic old town in the south & the awe-striking and serene coast in the north, the destination has something for everyone.

📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

node.text:
Charming snaps by @enrico_costantini from Palazzo Daniele. 😍 Crossing amazing architecture by Dominico Malinconico and interior design by Ludovica and Roberto Palomba of Palomba Serafini, Palazzo Daniele is a feast for the eyes. Would you like to have an authentic experience inside an Italian palazzo? 🇮🇹 

The Petrucci family opened the palazzo's doors and turned it into a nine-suite guesthouse for vacationers and art lovers. If you're a fan of minimalism, ceiling frescoes, art, and warm Italian hospitality, this is where you should be! Lounge by the orange grove, admire the many art pieces all over the property, or even swap stories with the chef while she prepares an Apulian meal! 😋

Have you stayed in a palazzo? Who will you be bringing with you here? ❤️

📸 @enrico_costantini @palombaserafini
📍 @palazzodaniele Gagliano Del Capo, Italy

Experience the good life with @where.to.find.me at Masseria Torre Coccaro! 😍 Surrounded by ancient olive groves, this tower used to be part of a line of defense that has now has been restored into a 5-star country house. With gorgeous suites and warm Italian hospitality, your stay here will feel so close to home that'll make you want to stay longer. ❤️

💡 BH Tip: During summer, join their Festa Di Paese and special nights at their antique square! Attend their special grill nights, watch a movie under the stars on the Maroc terrace with views of the sea and Puglian sunset, and have a lavish feast at long communal tables with your Italian favorites freshly served! 😋

Have you visited Masseria Torre Coccaro? Would you like to stay here? 

📽️ @where.to.find.me
📍 @masseriatorrecoccaro, Italy
🎶 Fausto Papetti - La dolce vita

Getting into a holiday mood with @henri.arnulphy at one of the villas at Constance Hotels Moofushi. 🌊 Get barefoot chic in their spacious villas with décor and amenities that elevate your stay. Who's up for marveling at views of the Indian Ocean?

Bask in the glow of this peachy sunset with @helloomelissa. 🌅 Stylish quarters with dramatic views of the caldera are a norm at the Phos The Boutique Hotel Santorini. Enjoy private heated pools, delightful gastronomy, and exquisite offerings that truly make you feel like gods and goddesses during your stay!

Looking for activities around the property? Visit the Akrotiri Lighthouse and feel the culture and myth flow through you as you stand in one of the most important landmarks in all of Greece. Immerse yourself in history while exploring the Akrotiri Archaeological Site, where ruins are impressively preserved. 🇬🇷

When was the last time you visited Greece? How as your last stay?

📽️ @helloomelissa
📍 @phos_santorini, Santorini, Greece

node.text:
Gorgeous resort views by @caracarl at the Laucala Island Resort. 🏝 This private tropical paradise nestled among coconut plantations is your ultimate social distancing destination in the South Pacific! 🇫🇯

Thinking of exploring this island resort? Laucala's activities range from relaxing to adventurous. Tee off at their golf course which was thoughtfully designed to be integrated with the land's natural curves. Head to the Dive Centre and begin your journey to meet angelfish and hawksbill turtles while snorkeling, and end your day at the Spa Garden for some holistic therapy! 💆‍♀️

Have you been to Laucala? Is Fiji on your bucket list? ✈

📸 @caracarl
📍@laucalaisland, Fiji

Breathtaking poolside and ocean views by @dan_a_t! 🌊 Having breakfast on the edge of a glass-bottomed sky pool extending six meters over the cliff edge is indeed an unforgettable experience at The Edge Bali! 😍

This multi-awarded resort gives you incredible views, impeccable hospitality, and plenty of offers that fit whatever mood or vibe you're feeling.

On your stay:
1. Take your downtime at The Spa which clings to the rock face of a stunning 500-ft sea cliff.
2. Challenge yourself with a workout at their gym and focus on your goals with 180° views of the Indian Ocean.
3. Try their in-villa dinner served by your very own personal butler!

Would you like to stay here? Is Bali on your travel list? ☀️

node.text:
Be mesmerized by centuries-old views like @michaeltheexplorer at the Marvel Stone Hotel. 🇪🇬 Located across the street from the Entrance of Giza, the hotel offers spectacular views of the Three Great Pyramids & the Sphinx from its rooftop. How's this for a morning view? ❤️

Curious about pyramids? Here are some awesome facts about them!
1. The pyramids were once the tallest human-built structures.
2. There are actually more than a hundred pyramids in Egypt!
3. The Great Pyramid of Giza weighs an estimated 5,750,000 tons. 
4. Not all pyramids are pointed! 
5. We still don't know why they were built, but there are so many theories!

Have you visited the Great Pyramids? Is Egypt on your bucket list? 

📸 @michaeltheexplorer
📍 @marvelstonehotel, Cairo, Egypt

Let @oddproduzioni give you eco-glamping vibes at Iuta Glamping and Farm! 🍃 A glamour camping stay with luxury lodges, it's a serene retreat where you're fully surrounded by the natural beauty of century-old olive trees and a lemon plantation. 😍 

Being here will give you the feeling of living in full contact with the nature that surrounds you without having to give up on any comfort. The camp also adopts an eco-sustainable lifestyle and doesn’t use chemicals products. If you're aiming for an environment-friendly vacation, Iuta should definitely be at the top of your list! 🌱

Are eco-stays something you'd want to experience? Would you stay here? 

📸 @oddproduzioni
📍 @iutafarm, Syracuse, Italy
